OL,3,CSamaritans to close more than 100
OL,4,Cbranches under new plans
OL,6,FSuicide prevention charity Samaritans
OL,7,Fcould close more than half of its
OL,8,Fbranches under new proposals.
OL,10,FThe plans, which the charity says
OL,11,Fwould help to increase service
OL,12,Fcapacity, would see more than 100
OL,13,Fbranches closed across the UK and
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,FThe charity, founded in 1953, connects
OL,17,Ftrained volunteers with people who may
OL,18,Fbe struggling, with the organisation
OL,19,Festimating it answers a call for help
OL,20,Fevery ten seconds.
