OL,4,Cbranches under new plans
OL,6,FIt is understood there is no confirmed
OL,7,Fnumber for how many branches or which
OL,8,Flocations could be shut, but
OL,9,Fvolunteers have been told it is likely
OL,10,Fto be around half.
OL,12,FBut its Chief Executive Officer, Julie
OL,13,FBentley, said the current operation is
OL,14,F"not sustainable".
OL,16,F"Samaritans provides a life-saving
OL,17,Fservice, day and night, 365 days a
OL,18,Fyear, but the changing needs of our
OL,19,Fcallers and volunteers means thinking
OL,20,Fdifferently about the way our services
OL,21,Fneed to work," she said in a statement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
