OL,3,CSamaritans to close more than 100
OL,4,Cbranches under new plans
OL,6,F"We are engaging with our volunteers
OL,7,Fon proposed improvements that will
OL,8,Fmean we are able to answer more calls,
OL,9,Fhave more volunteers on duty, and be
OL,10,Fthere for more people in their darkest
OL,11,Fmoments.
OL,13,F"Samaritans volunteers are hugely
OL,14,Fdedicated to being there for our
OL,15,Fcallers and they remain at the heart
OL,16,Fof our service, but it is increasingly
OL,17,Fclear that having over 200 branches,
OL,18,Fvarying in size from 10 to 300
OL,19,Fvolunteers, is not sustainable and
OL,20,Fhinders us providing the best possible
OL,21,Fservice to the people who need us."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
