OL,11,FThe charity says it is consulting with
OL,12,Fvolunteers on the plans over the next
OL,13,Ffew months. Under the proposals,
OL,14,Fremaining branches would be scaled up
OL,15,Fand have their volunteer capacity
OL,16,Fincreased.
