OL,4,Cbranches under new plans
OL,6,FIt is also piloting a scheme which
OL,7,Fwould allow volunteers to take calls
OL,8,Fremotely, which the charity says could
OL,9,Fmake it easier for volunteers to give
OL,10,Ftheir time.
OL,12,FAll proposals would be subject to
OL,13,Fboard approval. Samaritans said the
OL,14,Fboard is due to meet later this year,
OL,15,Fand will begin implementing decisions
OL,16,Ffrom April in the UK.
